iio: chemical: sps30: fix missing triggered buffer dependency

SPS30 uses triggered buffer, but the dependency is not specified in the
Kconfig file.  Fix this by selecting IIO_BUFFER and IIO_TRIGGERED_BUFFER
config symbols.

